    <header>
    </header>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="page-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a365d 0%, #2b6cb0 100%) !important;">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 style="color: #ffffff !important; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">Partner Companies</h1>
            <p style="color: #ffffff !important; text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); opacity: 1;">Our Embroidery Partners</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partners Content -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 50px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    We are proud to collaborate with a diverse network of embroidery companies, each bringing their own unique set of skills, experiences, and specialties. This page is dedicated to highlighting our valuable partners, with whom we share a common vision of excellence, innovation, and commitment to quality.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="partners-grid">
                
                <div class="partner-card">
                    <img src="images/partners/barudan.png" alt="Barudan America, Inc">
                    <h3>Barudan America, Inc</h3>
                    <p>Barudan America, Inc. is a leading manufacturer of premium embroidery machines, continuing a tradition of Japanese excellence since 1959. Known for their precision engineering, innovative technology, and exceptional reliability, Barudan machines are trusted by embroidery professionals worldwide.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="partner-card">
                    <img src="images/partners/tajima.png" alt="Tajima Industries Ltd.">
                    <h3>Tajima Industries Ltd.</h3>
                    <p>Tajima Industries Ltd. is a renowned manufacturer of industrial embroidery machines, known for pioneering advancements in the field. The company has a significant global presence, supplying over 3,000 embroidery machines to more than 130 countries.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.tajima.com/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px 20px;">Visit Website</a>
                </div>

                <div class="partner-card">
                    <img src="images/partners/hoopmaster.jpg" alt="HoopMaster">
                    <h3>HoopMaster</h3>
                    <p>HoopMaster, operated by Midwest Products, Inc., specializes in providing innovative embroidery hooping devices designed to simplify and improve the embroidery process. Their Mighty Hoop magnetic hooping device is known for its ease of use and efficiency.</p>
                    <a href="https://hoopmaster.com/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px 20px;">Visit Website</a>
                </div>

                <div class="partner-card">
                    <img src="images/partners/embroiderytech.jpg" alt="Your Embroidery Tech">
                    <h3>Your Embroidery Tech</h3>
                    <p>Owned and operated by David Middleton, a seasoned veteran in the embroidery industry. David brings a wealth of experience from his tenure at a major embroidery machine company in Charlotte, NC. He manages an active Facebook community for embroidery professionals.</p>
                    <a href="https://yourembrioderytech.godaddysites.com/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px 20px;">Visit Website</a>
                </div>

                <div class="partner-card">
                    <img src="images/partners/wilcom.webp" alt="Wilcom">
                    <h3>Wilcom</h3>
                    <p>Wilcom is recognized as a global leader in embroidery digitizing software, catering to professional digitizers, embroidery shops, industry educators, and hobbyists since 1979. Their innovative software solutions like EmbroideryStudio offer advanced design and digitizing capabilities.</p>
                    <a href="https://wilcom.com/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px 20px;">Visit Website</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partnership CTA -->
    <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%); padding: 60px 0; color: white; text-align: center;">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Ready to Partner with Puncher?</h2>
            <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 30px; opacity: 0.9;">
                Join our global network of embroidery professionals! We're looking for companies worldwide to collaborate through link exchange, cross-promotion, and joint marketing opportunities.
            </p>
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 30px;">
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Benefits of partnering with us:</h4>
                <ul style="list-style: none; text-align: left; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">✅ Reach our international customer base</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">✅ Boost your SEO through link exchange</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">✅ Joint marketing and promotional opportunities</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">✅ Technical knowledge sharing and support</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-primary">Apply for Partnership</a>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.8; font-size: 14px;">We typically respond to partnership applications within 3-5 business days.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

